    "303c88053fcf0e8b": {
      "id": "303c88053fcf0e8b",
      "text": "### DeepSeek API Issues\n- **Problem:** DeepSeek API error \"Missing reasoning_content field\" when using thinking mode\n- **Root cause:** OpenClaw integration not fully compatible with DeepSeek's thinking mode API requirements\n- **Solution:** Switched to Claude Sonnet 4-6 model\n- **Lesson:** Different model providers have unique API requirements; need fallback options",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 131,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.988417",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "a67ff49d388e8483": {
      "id": "a67ff49d388e8483",
      "text": "### Async Agent Pattern Implementation\n- **Problem:** Session-fragile operations (Claude CLI, browser automation, long-running tasks) break on session termination\n- **Solution:** Externalized state pattern with queue system\n- **Implementation:** `async-agent-pattern` skill with JSONL queues and heartbeat processing\n- **Architecture:** Intent → Queue → Checkpoint → Process → Store → Resume\n- **Timeouts:** Claude messages (120s), Background jobs (600s), API calls (service-specific)",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 138,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.988445",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "9b5b70e5dbf52370": {
      "id": "9b5b70e5dbf52370",
      "text": "### Memory Visualization System (01-03-2026)\n- **Purpose:** Web interface for visualizing and exploring OpenClaw memory files\n- **Features:**\n  1. Timeline view of memory entries with filtering\n  2. Full-text search across all memory content\n  3. Statistics dashboard with interactive charts\n  4. Topic analysis and frequency visualization\n  5. Memory content viewer with detailed display\n- **Technology Stack:**\n  - Backend: Flask (Python) with REST API",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 148,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.988470",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "c4b7f6427e6508e3": {
      "id": "c4b7f6427e6508e3",
      "text": "- Frontend: Bootstrap 5, Chart.js, custom dark theme\n  - Data: JSON export from memory parser\n- **Access:** `http://localhost:5000` (run from `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory-viz/`)\n- **API Endpoints:** `/api/memory-data`, `/api/timeline`, `/api/search`, `/api/stats`, `/api/refresh`\n- **Data Sources:** MEMORY.md + memory/*.md files\n- **Current Stats:** 5 daily files, 34 entries, 1906 words, 369-day range\n4. **System Diagnostics:** Identified and fixed Moltbook cron issues (pending fix)\n5. **Gateway Configuration:** Fixed token mismatch, enabled entrosana.com access",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 157,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.988498",
