    "cda88f732678a5ba": {
      "id": "cda88f732678a5ba",
      "text": "### Notion Browser Bridge\n- **Problem:** Notion API changed 03-09-2025 - no more simple Internal Integrations, only OAuth-based Public Integrations\n- **Solution:** Browser automation via Chrome DevTools Protocol (CDP port 9223)\n- **Implementation:** `notion-browser-bridge.skill` for Notion access without OAuth\n- **Success:** Accessed Notion page \"MA Kooperation\", extracted content and screenshots",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 204,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.988631",
      "embedding_shape": [
