    "680f42354c346d7c": {
      "id": "680f42354c346d7c",
      "text": "### Gateway Configuration Updates\n- **entrosana.com access:** Added to `gateway.controlUi.allowedOrigins`\n- **Token synchronization:** Fixed mismatch between `gateway.auth.token` and `gateway.remote.token`\n- **Token restored:** `1f3c0559f9362ff5ff458c69eed348f6df5a7ec55bbc1287` (matches entrosana.com UI Control Settings)\n- **Result:** entrosana.com can now connect to this OpenClaw gateway",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
