    "be1290d5cb59fca4": {
      "id": "be1290d5cb59fca4",
      "text": "### E5-small-v2 Semantic Search Implementation\n- **Status**: Fully functional embedding engine with semantic understanding\n- **Model**: `intfloat/e5-small-v2` (384-dimensional embeddings)\n- **Multilingual support**: Successfully searches German thesis content\n- **Integration**: Standalone wrapper (`e5_memory_search_wrapper.py`) due to OpenClaw context size limitations\n- **Performance**: First query ~30s (model load), subsequent queries instant\n- **Chunks**: 256 tokens with 64 overlap (E5-optimized, not OpenClaw default)",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 665,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.989890",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "8e3a652e580f5870": {
      "id": "8e3a652e580f5870",
      "text": "### LangGraph Daily Memory Organization\n- **Cron job**: `0 20 * * *` (8 PM UTC / 3 PM Colombia time)\n- **Script**: `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/organize_langgraph_daily.sh`\n- **Tasks**: Semantic embeddings update, relationship computation, memory health report\n- **Notification**: Telegram \"library sorted\" on success (target: 1134139785)\n- **Test runs**: Successful with Telegram message IDs 3986, 3990\n- **Logs**: `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/logs/langgraph-daily-YYYY-MM-DD.log`",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
