    "841eeae4bac8c162": {
      "id": "841eeae4bac8c162",
      "text": "### PDF Translation Capability\n- **Challenge**: Spanish police report to German with visual layout preservation\n- **Tools**: pdfplumber (extraction), translate library (translation), FPDF (generation)\n- **Issues**: Text extraction line breaks, mixed Spanish/German in narrative\n- **Output**: `german_police_report.pdf` (form labels translated, data preserved)\n- **Lesson**: PDF form layout replication is complex; focus on information accuracy over visual perfection",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 681,
      "line_end": 687,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.989957",
      "embedding_shape": [
