    "c7c46311fc6dfc08": {
      "id": "c7c46311fc6dfc08",
      "text": "### Integration Principle: \"Don't Fight OpenClaw, Work With It\"\n- **Problem**: OpenClaw memory search integration failed due to context size mismatch\n- **Solution**: Created standalone E5 RAG system with HTTP service bridge pattern\n- **Skill**: Created `openclaw-integration-principle` documenting the approach\n- **Key insight**: When OpenClaw constraints block integration, build standalone and bridge via HTTP",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 693,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.989978",
      "embedding_shape": [
