    "840eeaa0d418322c": {
      "id": "840eeaa0d418322c",
      "text": "#### Portfolio Structure Integration\n- **Arjun.lol inspiration**: Implemented six-category portfolio system (Writing, Notes, Simulations, Art, Reading, CV) following academic portfolio best practices\n- **Date format standardization**: European format (dd-mm-YYYY) in all text, ISO format (YYYY-MM-DD) for filenames\n- **Enhanced PROJECT.md**: Restructured with clear category separation, integrated BA thesis 16-week schedule, maintained client project details\n- **Category directories**: Created dedicated directories for each portfolio category",
