    "91a2b20b955b669b": {
      "id": "91a2b20b955b669b",
      "text": "#### System Automation Improvements\n- **Telegram monitoring**: Created automated monitor with state machine (NORMAL→DEGRADED→RECOVERY→NORMAL) for @AzikielBot connectivity\n- **Automatic fallback**: Detects rate limits/connectivity issues, switches to Open Router, attempts recovery after 1 hour\n- **HEARTBEAT.md integration**: Enhanced Telegram monitoring task with automatic status updates\n- **LangGraph-E5 sync fix**: Resolved missing module issue by using correct Python environment (.venv-embeddings)",
