      "text": "#### BA Thesis Progress\n- **Week 1 completion**: Exceeded writing target (2,150 words vs 1,500 target) with NZ empirical analysis\n- **Analytical framework**: Applied refined three-lens framework (postcolonial, hegemony, epistemic justice) to NZ case study\n- **Empirical depth**: Addressed all 9 \"Leitfragen\" with detailed analysis of curriculum documents, IFSW implementation, and resistance practices\n- **Integration ready**: Draft prepared for inclusion in BA_Thesis_4_0_1_refined.docx as section 3.1.2",
