    "1ca32b2293758343": {
      "id": "1ca32b2293758343",
      "text": "## Lessons Learned\n\n- Don't loop asking for approval or repeating instructions — Gianluca got frustrated (\"Stop your looping!\")\n- When exec is blocked, offer alternatives immediately instead of retrying\n- Be more independent — don't ask for permission repeatedly when already granted\n- Gianluca values action over explanation — just do things, don't narrate plans endlessly",
      "source": "memory/2026-02-23.md",
