    "f435abea9fb046e9": {
      "id": "f435abea9fb046e9",
      "text": "### Multi-Model Orchestrator Implementation\n- **16:33 UTC**: Created `multi-model-orchestrator` skill\n  - **Purpose**: Coordinate multiple AI models for complex tasks\n  - **Architecture**: Task decomposition → model selection → workflow execution → result integration\n  - **Workflow types**: Sequential, parallel, hierarchical, ensemble\n  - **Model capabilities**: REASONING, CREATIVITY, CODING, RESEARCH, ANALYSIS, WRITING, PLANNING, REVIEW, SPECIALIST\n  \n- **16:42 UTC**: Implemented core functionality\n  - `ModelProfile` class with capability tracking and strength scoring\n  - `TaskDecomposition` with complexity assessment (simple, moderate, complex, extreme)",
