      "text": "### **Self-Repair Capability Established:**\nNow equipped to diagnose and fix dashboard connectivity issues independently using documented procedures and diagnostic scripts.\n\n**Timestamp**: 02-03-2026 23:38 UTC (18:38 Bogotá)\n**Status**: Dashboard crisis resolved, comprehensive documentation created, system fully operational",
