      "id": "72a8f4b72119a3e4",
      "text": "#### **Technical Specifications:**\n- **Model**: intfloat/e5-small-v2\n- **Parameters**: ~118 million\n- **Embedding dimension**: 384\n- **Multilingual**: Yes (supports 100+ languages)\n- **Prefix requirement**: E5 models need \"query: \" or \"passage: \" prefix\n- **Performance**: ~100 sentences/second on CPU",
