      "id": "a787a6263e93e724",
      "text": "#### **1. Improved Error Detection Patterns:**\nUpdated `TAG_RULES` in `memory_tagger.py` and `enhanced_memory_graph.py`:",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-03.md",
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 27,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-05T06:01:50.993179",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
